---

flowchart TD
    %% Color coding: blue=frontend, green=AI, orange=backend, red=approval gate, purple=agent

    Start([New Inquiry]) --> Channel{Channel?}

    Channel -->|Web Chat| WebChat[ai-chat Edge Function]
    Channel -->|WhatsApp| WhatsApp[OpenClaw Gateway]
    Channel -->|Intake Wizard| Wizard[RentalsIntakeWizard.tsx]

    WebChat --> Extract
    WhatsApp --> Extract
    Wizard --> Extract

    Extract[/"STEP 1: Extract Profile<br/>(Gemini Flash)"/] --> CreateLead
    CreateLead[(STEP 2: Create Lead Row<br/>leads table)] --> Score

    Score{STEP 3: Quality Score}
    Score -->|"> 0.7 High"| FastTrack[Auto-search + Top 3 Results]
    Score -->|"0.4-0.7 Standard"| StdQueue[Standard Queue]
    Score -->|"< 0.4 Low"| Clarify[Request Clarification<br/>via OpenClaw]

    FastTrack --> SearchResults[Ranked Results<br/>with Hermes Scores]
    StdQueue --> SearchResults
    Clarify -->|User responds| Extract

    SearchResults --> SelectListing[Renter Selects Listing]
    SelectListing --> RequestShowing[Request Showing]

    RequestShowing --> CheckAvail[Check Host Availability]
    CheckAvail --> ProposeSlots[Propose 3 Time Slots]
    ProposeSlots --> RenterPicks[Renter Selects Slot]
    RenterPicks --> CreateShowing[(Create showings Row<br/>status=proposed)]

    CreateShowing --> NotifyHost[Notify Host via OpenClaw]
    NotifyHost --> ConfidenceCheck{AI Confidence >= 0.7?}
    ConfidenceCheck -->|Yes| AutoSend[Send Notification]
    ConfidenceCheck -->|No| ApprovalGate1{{"APPROVAL GATE<br/>Paperclip Review"}}
    ApprovalGate1 --> AutoSend

    AutoSend --> HostConfirms[Host Confirms<br/>status=confirmed]
    HostConfirms --> Reminders[T-24h + T-1h Reminders]
    Reminders --> ShowingHappens[Showing Occurs]
    ShowingHappens --> Feedback[Renter Rates 1-5]

    Feedback --> FeedbackCheck{Rating?}
    FeedbackCheck -->|"4-5 stars"| PromptApply["Prompt: Apply Now?"]
    FeedbackCheck -->|"2-3 stars"| SuggestAlternatives[Suggest Similar Listings]
    FeedbackCheck -->|"1 star"| RefineSearch[Refine Search Criteria]

    SuggestAlternatives --> SelectListing
    RefineSearch --> Extract
    PromptApply --> SubmitApp[Submit Application<br/>4-step wizard]

    SubmitApp --> AISummary[/"AI Generates<br/>Applicant Summary"/]
    AISummary --> ApprovalGate2{{"APPROVAL GATE<br/>Paperclip Spot-Check"}}
    ApprovalGate2 --> ForwardToHost[Forward to Landlord]
    ForwardToHost --> HostDecision{Landlord Decision}

    HostDecision -->|Accepted| LeaseGen[/"Hermes: Generate<br/>Lease Summary"/]
    HostDecision -->|Rejected| NotifyReject[Notify Renter + Suggest Others]

    LeaseGen --> BilingualSummary[Bilingual Summary<br/>EN/ES + Risk Flags]
    BilingualSummary --> RenterReviews[Renter Reviews Terms]
    RenterReviews --> AcceptTerms[Accept Terms]

    AcceptTerms --> PaymentIntent[Create Stripe Payment Intent<br/>first_month + deposit]
    PaymentIntent --> AmountCheck{Amount > $500<br/>or New Host?}
    AmountCheck -->|Yes| ApprovalGate3{{"APPROVAL GATE<br/>Paperclip Review"}}
    AmountCheck -->|No| ProcessPayment
    ApprovalGate3 --> ProcessPayment[Process Payment]

    ProcessPayment --> Webhook[Stripe Webhook<br/>payment-webhook Edge Fn]
    Webhook --> BookingCreated[(Booking Created<br/>status=confirmed)]

    BookingCreated --> CommissionSplit[Commission Split<br/>12% mdeai / 88% host]
    CommissionSplit --> Confirmations[Confirmations<br/>Email + WhatsApp to Both]
    Confirmations --> MoveInPrep[T-2 Days: Move-in Prep<br/>Keys + WiFi + Contacts]
    MoveInPrep --> Done([Tenant Moves In])

    NotifyReject --> SelectListing

